Purpose of Audit AI Token:
The Audit AI token serves as the backbone of a secure, AI-driven blockchain auditing ecosystem. It incentivizes security assessments, rewards ethical hacking, and facilitates seamless transactions within the platform, ensuring transparency and trust in smart contracts.

Benefits:
✅ **Enhanced Security** – Reduces vulnerabilities in smart contracts through AI-powered audits.
✅ **Investor Trust** – Builds confidence by providing verifiable audit reports.
✅ **Efficient & Cost-Effective** – Optimizes blockchain audits with AI, reducing time and expenses.
✅ **Decentralized & Transparent** – Ensures unbiased and tamper-proof auditing processes.
✅ **Seamless Integration** – Works across multiple blockchain networks for wide adoption.
